{"tid":506903,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"事實證明有競爭先有進步","createTime":"2017-12-22T16:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T18:30:10.000Z","uid":24998,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c199011cd3f4bc59db8f109a188a588ca45a9ab","tid":506903,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"早泄恃住同類型既壇得佢搞就唔撚理<br />\n一多個對手就快快手手改善個壇<br />\n呢邊連仔見個壇穩穩定定又唔撚理咁<br />\n對面登一出新野開始搶返客就急急腳出哂啲新功能<br />\n如果仲係一壇獨大應該呢世都唔會有人搞啲新野出黎益user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2461597ce36bba26354a049b7f617ed9fbb68b2","tid":506903,"uid":38539,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"連仔望仔其實都keep住整緊更新啲<br />\n不過係人手少先整得慢啫"},{"pid":"4623a851c177463c7f356533528898ba393368b7","tid":506903,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59f7956ae0c669055c8e0207a98c3578118927c6","tid":506903,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有味有冇味冇<br />\n<br />\n有有冇冇真係咁重要咩？<br />\n<br />\n人生好多野唔係話你想有就有想冇就冇<br />\n<br />\n好多時有就會冇左<br />\n<br />\n冇左又突然有返<br />\n<br />\n睇開d 啦年輕人<br />\n<br />\n有時有定冇並不重要<br />\n<br />\n重要既係你要相信<br />\n<br />\n當你相信佢有佢就有<br />\n<br />\n佢冇佢就冇<br />\n<br />\n人生不過如此‼️<br />\n<br />\n無謂咁執著有定冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2f7a3bc95283e55ba43e5815487d19c8615f99","tid":506903,"uid":152047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"同埋要keep住鞭策連尼住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7fd54a8518a9b3125b4d85161ff13c522ea47b","tid":506903,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"h